attributes.long-description:
The Force™ will be with you, always, in the Star Wars™ Pinball Season 1 Bundle! This special pack brings together 13 incredible digital pinball tables set in the Star Wars universe for one low price.

Each Star Wars™ Pinball table is lovingly crafted, featuring tons of exciting details and elements that no Star Wars fan will want to miss out on! The Star Wars™ Pinball Season 1 Bundle features the following tables and packs:

• Star Wars™ Pinball
Star Wars™: Episode V: - The Empire Strikes Back™
Star Wars™: The Clone Wars™
Boba Fett
• Star Wars™ Pinball: Balance of the Force
Darth Vader
Star Wars™: Episode VI: - Return of the Jedi™
Star Wars™: Starfighter Assault
• Star Wars™ Pinball: Heroes Within
Han Solo
Droids™
Star Wars™: Episode IV: - A New Hope™
• Star Wars™ Pinball: Star Wars Rebels™
• Star Wars™ Pinball: The Force Awakens™ Pack
Star Wars™: The Force Awakens™
Might of the First Order

Star Wars™ Pinball

Compatible with PlayStation®3.
To use this download, you will need , product code(s)
This product is playable in 2D or 3D. To enjoy stereoscopic 3D features, you will require a 3D TV that supports stereoscopic display and compatible 3D glasses.
512KB minimum space required
1 - 4 Players
DUALSHOCK®3 Vibration Function
HDTV screen resolution: 720p
Stereoscopic 3D compatible
Network Players: 2 - 4
PlayStation®Eye camera optional
